Oh well now - now when I come to think of it we had it very often, you see, it must have been cheaper than it is now. Yes, we had meaty meals quite often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14883545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2183528\charrsid6448569 How many times a week?
