Well, no, you didn't take much notice, did you, what your mother had - you just got on with what she gave you. But I remember my grandfather, my mother's -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14883545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2183528\charrsid6448569 Did your father have more?
