t talk or giggle you see. Scrape - he used to always say scrape your plates - used to say the one who - who cleans their plate most gets the most pudding, see, always said that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14883545 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2183528\charrsid6448569 
