at you'd call it - it was a long time ago. And we'd play rounders - four corners, - somebody'd hit a ball - rounders. And - we had - shuttle cock. 'Cos you know out in the summer you were out all the time. And we'd play hide and seek round the gardens and
 things. I can't remember the games - long - a long time since.
